#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:13
msgid ""
"fish no longer reads the terminfo database to alter behaviour based on the :"
"envvar:`TERM` environment variable, and does not depend on ncurses or "
"terminfo. The ``ignore-terminfo`` feature flag, introduced and enabled by "
"default in fish 4.1, is now permanently enabled. fish may no longer work "
"correctly on Data General Dasher D220 and Wyse WY-350 terminals, but should "
"continue to work on all known terminal emulators released in the 21st "
"century."
msgstr ""

