#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:73
msgid ""
"The ``abbr``, ``bind``, ``complete``, ``functions``, ``history`` and "
"``type`` commands now support a ``--color`` option to control syntax "
"highlighting in their output. Valid values are ``auto`` (default), "
"``always``, or ``never``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:74
msgid ""
"Existing file paths in redirection targets such as ``> file.txt`` are now "
"highlighted using :envvar:`fish_color_valid_path`, indicating that ``file."
"txt`` will be clobbered (:issue:`12260`)."
msgstr ""

