"Sample config file ``~/.config/fish/config.fish/`` and config directories "
"``~/.config/fish/conf.d/``, ``~/.config/fish/completions/`` and ``~/.config/"
"fish/functions/`` were recreated on every startup instead of only the first "
"time fish runs on a system (:issue:`12230`)."
