#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:351
msgid ""
"New documentation page :doc:`Terminal Compatibility <terminal-"
"compatibility>` (also accessible via ``man fish-terminal-compatibility``) "
"lists the terminal control sequences used by fish."
