#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3927
msgid "fish 2.3b2 (released May 5, 2016)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3934
msgid ""
"A new ``fish_realpath`` builtin and associated function to allow the use of "
"``realpath`` even on those platforms that don’t ship an appropriate command "
"(:issue:`2932`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3937
msgid ""
"Alt-# toggles the current command line between commented and uncommented "
"states, making it easy to save a command in history without executing it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3940
msgid ""
"The ``fish_vi_mode`` function is now deprecated in favour of "
"``fish_vi_key_bindings``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3948
msgid ""
"Fix the build on Cygwin (:issue:`2952`) and RedHat Enterprise Linux/CentOS 5 "
"(:issue:`2955`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3950
msgid ""
"Avoid confusing the terminal line driver with non-printing characters in "
"``fish_title`` (:issue:`2453`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3952
msgid ""
"Improved completions for busctl, git (:issue:`2585`, :issue:`2879`, :issue:"
"`2984`), and netctl."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3958
msgid "fish 2.3b1 (released April 19, 2016)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3963 ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:4242
#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:4342
msgid "Significant Changes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3965
msgid ""
"A new ``string`` builtin to handle… strings! This builtin will measure, "
"split, search and replace text strings, including using regular expressions. "
"It can also be used to turn lists into plain strings using ``join``. "
"``string`` can be used in place of ``sed``, ``grep``, ``tr``, ``cut``, and "
"``awk`` in many situations. (:issue:`2296`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3970
msgid ""
"Allow using escape as the Meta modifier key, by waiting after seeing an "
"escape character wait up to 300ms for an additional character. This is "
"consistent with readline (e.g. bash) and can be configured via the "
"``fish_escape_delay_ms variable``. This allows using escape as the Meta "
"modifier. (:issue:`1356`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3975
msgid ""
"Add new directories for vendor functions and configuration snippets (:issue:"
"`2500`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3977
msgid ""
"A new ``fish_realpath`` builtin and associated ``realpath`` function should "
"allow scripts to resolve path names via ``realpath`` regardless of whether "
"there is an external command of that name; albeit with some limitations. See "
"the associated documentation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3983 ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:4083
msgid "Backward-incompatible changes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3985
msgid ""
"Unmatched globs will now cause an error, except when used with ``for``, "
"``set`` or ``count`` (:issue:`2719`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3987
msgid ""
"``and`` and ``or`` will now bind to the closest ``if`` or ``while``, "
"allowing compound conditions without ``begin`` and ``end`` (:issue:`1428`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3989
msgid ""
"``set -ql`` now searches up to function scope for variables (:issue:`2502`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3990
msgid ""
"``status -f`` will now behave the same when run as the main script or using "
"``source`` (:issue:`2643`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3992
msgid ""
"``source`` no longer puts the file name in ``$argv`` if no arguments are "
"given (:issue:`139`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3994
msgid ""
"History files are stored under the ``XDG_DATA_HOME`` hierarchy (by default, "
"in ``~/.local/share``), and existing history will be moved on first use (:"
"issue:`744`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:4003
msgid "Fish no longer silences errors in config.fish (:issue:`2702`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../CHANGELOG.rst:4004
msgid ""
"Directory autosuggestions will now descend as far as possible if there is "
"only one child directory (:issue:`2531`)"
